es.uvigo.darwin.prottest.global.options
Class SerializableApplicationOptions

java.lang.Object
  es.uvigo.darwin.prottest.global.options.SerializableApplicationOptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SerializableApplicationOptions
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class is a serializable version of ApplicationOptions. It has all important attributes in a concrete state of the application, and reduces alignment ant topology to a hash, making this object much lighter than the Application Options instance.

Since:
3.0
